{"name":"祁奚荐贤","type":"诗词歌赋","description":"无","example":"君子谓祁奚于是能举善矣  其祁奚之谓矣 立其子不为比 晋侯曰孰可以代之 祁奚请老晋侯问嗣焉 ","words":[{"word":"伯华得官","pinyin":"bo'hua'de'guan"},{"word":"称解狐其仇也","pinyin":"cheng'jie'hu'qi'chou'ye"},{"word":"称其仇不为谄","pinyin":"cheng'qi'chou'bu'wei'chan"},{"word":"对曰赤也可","pinyin":"dui'yue'chi'ye'ke"},{"word":"对曰午也可","pinyin":"dui'yue'wu'ye'ke"},{"word":"夫唯善故能举其类","pinyin":"fu'wei'shan'gu'neng'ju'qi'lei"},{"word":"建一官而三物成","pinyin":"jian'yi'guan'er'san'wu'cheng"},{"word":"将立之而卒又问焉","pinyin":"jiang'li'zhi'er'zu'you'wen'yan"},{"word":"解狐得举祁午得位","pinyin":"jie'hu'de'ju'qi'wu'de'wei"},{"word":"晋侯曰孰可以代之","pinyin":"jin'hou'yue'shu'ke'yi'dai'zhi"},{"word":"举其偏不为党","pinyin":"ju'qi'pian'bu'wei'dang"},{"word":"君子谓祁奚于是能举善矣","pinyin":"jun'zi'wei'qi'xi'yu'shi'neng'ju'shan'yi"},{"word":"立其子不为比","pinyin":"li'qi'zi'bu'wei'bi"},{"word":"能举善也","pinyin":"neng'ju'shan'ye"},{"word":"其祁奚之谓矣","pinyin":"qi'qi'xi'zhi'wei'yi"},{"word":"祁奚请老晋侯问嗣焉","pinyin":"qi'xi'qing'lao'jin'hou'wen'si'yan"},{"word":"商书曰无偏无党王道荡荡","pinyin":"shang'shu'yue'wu'pian'wu'dang'wang'dao'dang'dang"},{"word":"是以似之祁奚有焉","pinyin":"shi'yi'si'zhi'qi'xi'you'yan"},{"word":"诗云惟其有之","pinyin":"shi'yun'wei'qi'you'zhi"},{"word":"羊舌赤佐之","pinyin":"yang'she'chi'zuo'zhi"},{"word":"于是使祁午为中军尉","pinyin":"yu'shi'shi'qi'wu'wei'zhong'jun'wei"},{"word":"于是羊舌职死矣","pinyin":"yu'shi'yang'she'zhi'si'yi"}]}